		<title>【ps基础】使用时间轴创建gif动画</title>
		<link>http://www.dyartstyle.com/1863.html</link>

		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<blockquote>最近发现很多做设计的朋友不会用ps的动画功能，Adobe在ps CS4系列的时候就已经吧动画功能集合在ps中，cs6以后的版本中又改成时间轴功能；

而且编者发现很多朋友会用帧动画做gif，但是不会用时间轴，今天，给大家写个小教程，用时间轴做个简单的小动画。</blockquote>
<h2>先上效果图</h2>
&nbsp;

<a href="http://dyartstyle.com/?attachment_id=1886" rel="attachment wp-att-1886"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1886" src="http://dyartstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/动画.gif" alt="动画" width="300" height="500" /></a>
<h2>这里使用PS CC演示</h2>
<a href="http://dyartstyle.com/?attachment_id=1864" rel="attachment wp-att-1864"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1864" src="http://dyartstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/QQ截图20160509171838.png" alt="QQ截图20160509171838" width="790" height="562" /></a>
<h2>一、首先打开PS，并在窗口菜单中选中时间轴，打开</h2>
<a href="http://dyartstyle.com/?attachment_id=1865" rel="attachment wp-att-1865"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1865" src="http://dyartstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/QQ截图20160509172055.png" alt="QQ截图20160509172055" width="1128" height="669" /></a>
<h2>二、创建300*500竖构图画布，分辨率72ppi，底色白色</h2>
<a href="http://dyartstyle.com/?attachment_id=1866" rel="attachment wp-att-1866"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1866" src="http://dyartstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/QQ截图20160509172216.png" alt="QQ截图20160509172216" width="555" height="366" /></a>
<h2>三、在画板顶部中心位置，使用形状工具新建一个圆，填充色（#9977cc,颜色随便写）</h2>
&nbsp;

<a href="http://dyartstyle.com/?attachment_id=1867" rel="attachment wp-att-1867"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1867" src="http://dyartstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/QQ截图20160509172957.png" alt="QQ截图20160509172957" width="362" height="553" /></a>
<h2>四、在时间轴面板中，点击中间“创建时间轴”按钮，出现时间轴界面</h2>
<a href="http://dyartstyle.com/?attachment_id=1868" rel="attachment wp-att-1868"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1868" src="http://dyartstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/QQ截图20160509173058.png" alt="QQ截图20160509173058" width="308" height="97" /></a>

<a href="http://dyartstyle.com/?attachment_id=1869" rel="attachment wp-att-1869"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1869" src="http://dyartstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/QQ截图20160509173324.png" alt="QQ截图20160509173324" width="660" height="228" /></a>
<h2>五、图层面板中选中圆所在图层，点击右键，将该图层转换成只能对象</h2>
<a href="http://dyartstyle.com/?attachment_id=1870" rel="attachment wp-att-1870"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1870" src="http://dyartstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/QQ截图20160509173602.png" alt="QQ截图20160509173602" width="275" height="432" /></a>
<h2>六、点击时间轴面板中，该图层标题前的小箭头，展开动画选项</h2>
<a href="http://dyartstyle.com/?attachment_id=1871" rel="attachment wp-att-1871"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1871" src="http://dyartstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/QQ截图20160509173915.png" alt="QQ截图20160509173915" width="611" height="240" /></a>
<h2>七、将时间轴指针拖到起始点00位置，点击变换前的计时器标识创建关键帧</h2>
<a href="http://dyartstyle.com/?attachment_id=1872" rel="attachment wp-att-1872"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1872" src="http://dyartstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/QQ截图20160509180218.png" alt="QQ截图20160509180218" width="632" height="231" /></a>
<h2>八、将指针拖至0-1s的5f位置，Ctrl+T自由变换圆形，自由变换中心点拖至圆的顶点中心位置，垂直缩放比例设置为120%，确定</h2>
<a href="http://dyartstyle.com/?attachment_id=1873" rel="attachment wp-att-1873"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1873" src="http://dyartstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/20160509181008.png" alt="20160509181008" width="908" height="321" /></a>
<h2>九、将指针拖至0-1s的10f位置，Ctrl+T自由变换圆形，自由变换中心点拖至圆的底边中心位置，垂直缩放比例设置为100%，确定</h2>
<a href="http://dyartstyle.com/?attachment_id=1875" rel="attachment wp-att-1875"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1875" src="http://dyartstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/QQ截图20160509181449.png" alt="QQ截图20160509181449" width="803" height="345" /></a>
<h2>十 、指针拖到1s位置，按Shift将圆拖到画布底边，与底边相切</h2>
<a href="http://dyartstyle.com/?attachment_id=1876" rel="attachment wp-att-1876"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1876" src="http://dyartstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/QQ截图20160509183011.png" alt="QQ截图20160509183011" width="505" height="864" /></a>
<h2>十一、将指针拖至1-2s的5f位置，Ctrl+T自由变换圆形，自由变换中心点拖至圆的底边中心位置，垂直缩放比例设置为80%，确定</h2>
<a href="http://dyartstyle.com/?attachment_id=1877" rel="attachment wp-att-1877"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1877" src="http://dyartstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/QQ截图20160509183259.png" alt="QQ截图20160509183259" width="745" height="698" /></a>
<h2>十二、将指针拖至1-2s的15f位置，Ctrl+T自由变换圆形，自由变换中心点拖至圆的底边中心位置，垂直缩放比例设置为120%，确定</h2>
&nbsp;

<a href="http://dyartstyle.com/?attachment_id=1879" rel="attachment wp-att-1879"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1879" src="http://dyartstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/QQ截图20160509183702.png" alt="QQ截图20160509183702" width="701" height="711" /></a>
<h2>十三、将指针拖至1-2s的20f位置，Ctrl+T自由变换圆形，自由变换中心点拖至圆的顶边中心位置，垂直缩放比例设置为100%，确定</h2>
<a href="http://dyartstyle.com/?attachment_id=1880" rel="attachment wp-att-1880"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1880" src="http://dyartstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/QQ截图20160509183941.png" alt="QQ截图20160509183941" width="658" height="694" /></a>
<h2>十四 、指针拖到2s-3s的10f位置，按Shift将圆拖到画布顶边，顶点与顶边相切</h2>
<a href="http://dyartstyle.com/?attachment_id=1881" rel="attachment wp-att-1881"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1881" src="http://dyartstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/QQ截图20160509184212.png" alt="QQ截图20160509184212" width="594" height="823" /></a>
<h2>十五、将指针拖至2-3s的15f位置，Ctrl+T自由变换圆形，自由变换中心点拖至圆的顶边中心位置，垂直缩放比例设置为80%，确定</h2>
<a href="http://dyartstyle.com/?attachment_id=1883" rel="attachment wp-att-1883"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1883" src="http://dyartstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/QQ截图20160509184508.png" alt="QQ截图20160509184508" width="709" height="292" /></a>
<h2>十六、将指针拖至2-3s的20f位置，Ctrl+T自由变换圆形，自由变换中心点拖至圆的顶边中心位置，垂直缩放比例设置为100%，确定</h2>
&nbsp;

<a href="http://dyartstyle.com/?attachment_id=1884" rel="attachment wp-att-1884"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1884" src="http://dyartstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/QQ截图20160509184719.png" alt="QQ截图20160509184719" width="767" height="319" /></a>
<h2>十七、此时动画关键帧已经设置完成，讲时间轴上的结束卡尺，拖到2-3s的20f位置,点击左侧的播放预览</h2>
<a href="http://dyartstyle.com/?attachment_id=1885" rel="attachment wp-att-1885"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1885" src="http://dyartstyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/QQ截图20160509185004.png" alt="QQ截图20160509185004" width="1001" height="226" /></a>

此时大家可以预览到用时间轴做的简单动画了。点击文件菜单，选择“存储为web所用格式”。导出为gif即可。
